Package: rumr
Title: Regression Uncertainty Modeler with R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = c("David", "Senhora"),
           family = "Navega",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "dsnavega@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4495-3762"))
Description: This package allows to construct predictive intervals for regression
        models by recasting uncertainty estimation itself as a regression problem.
        Currently implementing truncated gaussian, conformal prediction and local
        uncertainty estimation models.
